title: Humraaz
subTitle: A wealthy Raj Singhania begins an affair with Priya, an entertainer who already has a boyfriend. While they start their relationship, Priya's lover decides to get his revenge on them.

title: Humse Badhkar Kaun
subTitle: Two brothers, a villager and a petty but cunning fraud, help their estranged mother, the chief minister of the state, to oust her enemies and terrorists.

title: Mahabali Bal Ganesh VI
subTitle: Top, Dhoti and Suitboot land on Kailash Parbat where they meet Nandi and Mooshak Raj. There, they come across stories about Bal Ganesh, who fights to rid the world of demons.

title: Saajan
subTitle: Breaking conventional barriers, a poor, disabled orphan befriends the son of a wealthy businessman. However, their friendship is put to the test after both friends fall in love with the same woman.

title: Achanak
subTitle: A man is determined to prove his lover's innocence after she is suddenly accused of murdering his family.

title: Hum Aapke Dil Mein Rehte Hain
subTitle: Love begins with a marriage of convenience and stays with Megha and Vijay in the throes of separation. In a classic case of unfortunate timing, one realises it too soon, while the other is too late.

title: Dil Pardesi Ho Gayaa
subTitle: When Major Ram of the Indian Army is captured by the Pakistani military, his younger brother Sunny begins a daring mission to rescue him, only to find himself falling for a Pakistani woman.

title: Khuda Gawah
subTitle: Badshah Khan travels to India to behead the man who killed Benazir's father and win her hand in marriage. He succeeds in his mission but is caught by Ranveer Singh, a jailor.

title: Champion
subTitle: Rajveer, a police officer, is tasked with protecting a nine-year-old heir, Abbas. However, the job gets complicated when Nazir, a dangerous criminal, seeks to harm the child.

title: Champion

title: Kartoos
subTitle: ACP Jay Suryavanshi assigns an inmate on death row, Jeet, the task of killing Jagat, a terrorist. Things take a turn when Jeet falls in love with Mini and gets distracted from his mission.

title: Hanuman vs. Mahiravana
subTitle: Lord Hanuman goes to save Goddess Sita and defeat the king of Lanka, Ravana. To defend his kingdom, Ravana unleashes his most powerful ally, his brother, Mahiravana.

title: Jab Pyaar Kisise Hota Hai
subTitle: Sooraj Dhanrajgir, a playboy, falls in love with Komal, who rejects him because of his vices and gives him time to change. Things go awry when a little boy shows up claiming to be his son.

title: Jai Vikraanta
subTitle: When a poor, honest farmer from rural India is killed by a greedy landlord, his son, Vikraanta, takes a vow to avenge his murder.

title: Ghar Ghar Ki Kahani
subTitle: Ram begins to suspect that his wife, Seeta, is having an affair with his brother, Amar. His suspicion remains even after Amar gets married, creating problems within his family.

title: Himmatwala
subTitle: After being humiliated by an autocratic landlord, a temple priest kills himself. Later, the priest's son returns to the village seeking revenge.

title: Sholay
subTitle: Jai and Veeru, two ex-convicts, are hired by Thakur Baldev Singh, a retired policeman, to help him nab Gabbar Singh, a notorious dacoit, who has spread havoc in the village of Ramgarh.

title: Ram Jaane
subTitle: Ram Jaane, an orphan, grows up to be a criminal. His social worker friend tries to reform him but Ram is keener to win over his childhood love, Bela, than turning over a new leaf.

title: Ram Jaane

title: Aakhri Adalat
subTitle: An honest police officer decides to take the law into his own hands when he loses his job, and the thugs he caught get released due to some technicality.

title: Naina
subTitle: After years of blindness caused by an accident, Naina gets a successful cornea transplant. However, she soon begins to see terrifying visions that prompt her to investigate the source of her sight.

title: Betaab
subTitle: Betaab Is A Bollywood Action Hindi Romantic Movie, Directed By Rahul Rawail, Starring Sunny Deol, Amrita Singh And Shammi Kapoor In The Lead Roles. When Sunny Meets His Childhood Friend, Roma, Love Blossoms Between The Two. But Roma's Father Disapproves Of Their Relationship And Decides To Separate Them.

title: Ready
subTitle: A case of mistaken identities causes Prem and Sanjana to fall in love. Meanwhile, Sanjana's uncles try to get the money that she has inherited and Prem convinces them to marry her off to him.

title: Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge
subTitle: While travelling across Europe, Raj and Simran unexpectedly grow close, only to be separated by family expectations, prompting Raj to fight for love and tradition.

title: Kya Kehna
subTitle: A young university student's world is rocked when her brief involvement with a wealthy playboy results in her pregnancy.

title: Ghulam-E-Musthafa
subTitle: A notorious hitman forsakes a life of crime after his lady love suffers a tragic death due to his professional rivalries. However, the mafia compels him to return for a final hit job.

title: Dhol
subTitle: Four lazy friends want to make easy money and aim to marry a rich girl. Their plan backfires after they meet Ritu and get embroiled with a dangerous criminal.
